List resources for a package

Source: R/list_package_resources.R
list_package_resources.Rd

List resources for a package

list_package_resources(package)

Arguments

package

A way to identify the package. Either a package ID (passed as a character vector directly) or a single package resulting from list_packages or search_packages

Examples

# NOT RUN {
list_package_resources("1db34737-ffad-489d-a590-9171d500d453")
# }
